This way, this way, this way!

\n<Rui>...I need to calm down. If I believe what that
demon said, this is all a game. There shouldn't be
such a thing as not being able to clear it.

\n<Rui>Every time I got through the monster's space, I
ended up back at school...

\n<Rui>Right now, I was just about to pass through the
entrance...

\n<Rui>Which means, if I get through here, I'll be
outside the entrance... It should be the goal!
\n<Rui>...I'll show them that I can escape.
\n<Rui>I've come this far, I should be able to do it!
\n<Rui>Huh... that iron gate over there opened too?
\n<Rui>Which one is the right way, I wonder?

\n<Rui>What's this voice... it's resonating in my head...
it feels nasty...
If you're tied up, you can't be eaten.
It feels good to open up a hole.
It's fun to hear you cry and struggle.
You seem soft, must feel nice.
You smell so good, hurry up.

\n<Rui>I have to run... That thing can't be reasoned
with...
The more you're scared, the tastier you become.

The more you're violated, the more delightful it
becomes.
You seem like you'd cry a lot... Ahh.
I want to eat, eat, eat, eat!
\n<Rui>That one, I absolutely must not get caught by it.
